A4M相信将一些干预手段组合起来，可以产生“抗衰老转换”。这些手段包括[[激素|激素]]、[[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]、生活方式调整和锻炼。<ref name=A4MPdf>{{cite web | last = Goldman | first = R | coauthors = Klatz R | url = http://www.worldhealth.net/pdf/Goldman,Klatz_intl-PRINT.pdf | title = Anti-Aging Medicine: An Introduction to the World’s Fastest-Growing Medical Specialty | format = pdf | publisher = American Academy of Anti-Aging Medicine | accessdate = December 16, 2009 | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100119193936/http://www.worldhealth.net/pdf/Goldman,Klatz_intl-PRINT.pdf | archivedate = 2010-01-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>2002年Klatz的一份报告强调了在维持老年健康方面被广泛推荐的许多干预手段，例如保持纤瘦、避免吸烟、规律锻炼、维持积极的社交生活和性生活、持续的思维刺激、避免压力、健康饮食、适度饮酒。这份报告还推荐服用抗氧化补充剂，以及避免喝自来水，称其“危险”，因为其被有毒化学物质污染。<ref>{{cite web|last=Fontenot|first=Cliff|title=Interview With Dr Ronald Klatz|url=http://www.anti-aging-source.com/dr-ronald-klatz.html|work=Interview With Dr. Ronald Klatz|publisher=Anti Aging Source|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GjlaRAhH?url=http://www.anti-aging-source.com/dr-ronald-klatz.html|archivedate=2013-05-19}}</ref>A4M争辩称这些干预手段的组合应用可以实现“现实的永生”，将人类寿命延长至超过150岁，还预言在3000年之前可以超过200岁。<ref name=KlatzPdf>{{cite web | last = Klatz | first = R | url = http://www.worldhealth.net/pdf/Tips_Antiaging.PDF | format = pdf | title = Anti-Aging Medicine | publisher = American Academy of Anti-Aging Medicine | accessdate = December 16, 2009 | year = 2002 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615170122/http://www.worldhealth.net/pdf/Tips_Antiaging.PDF | archivedate = 2011年6月15日 }}</ref>2006年，Klatz在一段文字中预言，这种寿命的戏剧性的增长将由诸如[[纳米技术|纳米技术]]、[[干细胞|干细胞]]疗法等技术的浮现而产生，他声称这将“显现出对于所有——从中风到脊髓损伤——的普遍性的希望”。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.worldhealth.net/news/forever_young_the_scientific_fountain_of/ | title = Forever Young: The Scientific Fountain of Youth | publisher = American Academy of Anti-Aging Medicine | date = February 22, 2006 | accessdate =December 16, 2009 }}</ref>Klatz相信在未来实现这些技术发现之后，“人类将进化进入不老的社会，我们将具有无限的肉体与精神活力”。<ref name=Garreau/>

